# Common Cron Schedule Examples:
# */15 * * * * - Every 15 minutes
# 0 9-17 * * 1-5 - Every hour from 9 AM to 5 PM, Monday to Friday
# 0 */2 * * * - Every 2 hours
# 30 9 * * * - Daily at 9:30 AM
# 0 0 * * * - Daily at midnight